---
layout: bento.njk
title: Topics
seo_title: Blog Topics | Jenish Jain's Engineering Blog
description: Explore engineering blog posts by topic — Kafka, system design, automation, productivity, and more.
permalink: /tags/
---

<main class="tags-page">

  <div class="tags-header">
    <div class="tags-kicker">/topics</div>
    <h1 class="tags-title">Browse by topic</h1>
    <p class="tags-sub">{{ description }}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="tags-grid">
    {% for tag in tagList %}
      {% set tagPosts = [] %}
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        {% if post.data.tags and post.data.tags.includes(tag.name) %}
          {% set tagPosts = tagPosts.concat([post]) %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      {% if tagPosts | length > 0 %}
      <a class="tag-tile" href="/tag/{{ tag.slug }}/">
        <div class="tag-tile-name">#{{ tag.name }}</div>
        <div class="tag-tile-count">{{ tagPosts | length }} post{% if tagPosts | length != 1 %}s{% endif %}</div>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</main>

<style>
  .tags-page {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(20px, 4vw, 48px) 80px;
  }

  .tags-header {
    padding: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px) 0 clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hair);
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .tags-kicker {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .tags-kicker::before {
    content: "";
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }
  .tags-title {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .tags-sub {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tags-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .tag-tile {
    background: var(--tile);
    border: 1px solid var(--hair);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 22px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    min-height: 110px;
    transition: transform .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), box-shadow .3s, background .2s;
  }
  .tag-tile:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    background: var(--accent);
  }
  .tag-tile-name {
    font-family: var(--display);
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 24px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .tag-tile-count {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
</style>
